item.title: About me
item.description: Hi there! I am a graduate student at Imperial College London pursuing an MSc in Computing with specialism in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning. Recently, I joined the Brain and Behaviour Lab working under the supervision of Professor Aldo Faisal on Reinforcement Learning control. I have a diverse set of interests. Currently, I am particularly interested in how we can leverage our understanding of human locomotion to develop better control algorithms.
